    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make large venues offer hygienic spaces for disabled medical needs",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Change the law to require large venues to provide dedicated, hygienic spaces for disabled people to manage medical needs beyond just standard toilet facilities. This would include safe areas for tube feeding or medication use. We believe this will ensure dignity, safety, and accessibility for all.",
